    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Waskita Beton Precast Tbk engages in the manufacture and sale of precast and ready-mix concrete in Indonesia. It operates through Precast, Readymix, and Construction Services segments. The company provides box and PC-I girders, spun and square piles, full slabs, rail road bearings, beam-column, box culverts, CCSPs, electric poles, FCSPs and FRSPs, half slabs, hollow core slabs, linings, moveable concrete barriers, PC-T and PC-U girders, RC pipes, RISHA modifications, precast house type 36 and modular precast house type 45 products, sloofs, SPRigWP, tetrapods, U-ditches and covers, and voided slabs. It also offers construction, engineering, installation, erection, and post-tensioning services. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Jakarta Timur, Indonesia. PT Waskita Beton Precast Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Waskita Karya (Persero) Tbk.",
